SteamFi
=======

This plugin allows sending SMS messages using steam.fi SMS gateway.


Example
=======

# Put API configuration into config/initializers/steam_fi.rb
SteamFi::API.setup(
  :username => 'someuser', 
  :password => 'somepassword'
)

# Then use in your controller
SteamFi::API.send_sms('1234PHONE', 'Hello world')


